The blaze broke out nearly a week ago in the Rust en Vrede Waterfall area, which is situated about 25km from Oudtshoorn. CAPE TOWN A veld fire is still raging in the mountains north of Oudtshoorn. The blaze broke out nearly a week ago in the Rust en Vrede Waterfall area, which is situated about 25 kilometres from Oudtshoorn. The Eden district municipality s Wouter Jacobs says, At the stage the fire is only in the mountains; the people can t get to it. We have people placed in strategic [areas]. 